            flag = False
            new_sequence += '0'

        else:
            new_sequence += '0'
    return new_sequence
```
This function goes through the sequence, when it finds the first non-zero digit, it sets a flag, then it replaces every digit after that until the next zero with 8. It repeats this process until it reaches the end of the sequence.

